

vulntrack/
├── main.py                 ← FastAPI app entry point
├── requirements.txt        ← pip dependencies
├── .env                    ← MySQL credentials 
├── README.md               ← Setup guide
├── sql/schema.sql          ← Full MySQL schema + seed data
└── app/
